<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/5" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h1 id="toc0"><span>Automated Passive Amnestization System Ver. 17.09</span></h1>
<p><strong><a href="http://scpper.com/page/789889960">Stats</a> <span style="color: grey">|</span> <a href="http://scpexplained.wikidot.com/apas">Explained</a></strong></p>
</div>
<hr />
<p><strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721473" alt="Nagiros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;">Nagiros</a></span>, now with <strong><a href="/nagiros">an author page</a></strong>.</p>
<p><strong>Shoutouts:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2893766&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721473" alt="Croquembouche" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2893766)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;">Croquembouche</a></span>, for writing the extremely helpful <a href="/listpages-magic-and-you">ListPages Magic and You</a> guide.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calamitous1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4780073); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4780073&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721473" alt="calamitous1" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4780073)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calamitous1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4780073); return false;">calamitous1</a></span>, for providing a critique in the <a href="/forum/t-11168832/tale:site-wide-behavioral-control#post-4220273">Drafts and Critique forum</a>.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p><strong>Image Credits:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>File name &quot;dro-0001&quot; taken from <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/nve/8733992389/">NVE's Flickr</a>, who allows all images of theirs to be used with credit.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p><strong>Stuff You May Also Like:</strong> <span style="font-size:75%;">For this tale it's more like &quot;Stuff I Ripped Formatting From&quot;.</span></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2798">SCP-2798</a>, by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2203795&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721473" alt="Kalinin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2203795)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;">Kalinin</a></span></li>
<li><a href="/tanhony-s-proposal">SCP-001: Dead Men</a>, by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(776854); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721473" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(776854); return false;">Tanhony</a></span></li>
<li><a href="/scp-3942">UNDEFINED</a>, by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jack-ike" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1618170); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1618170&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721473" alt="Jack Ike" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1618170)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jack-ike" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1618170); return false;">Jack Ike</a></span></li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p>Thanks a ton, all!</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div class="creditBottomRate" style="position:relative;height:30px;">
